---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Speaking & Workshops — Haider Ali"
  description="Book Haider Ali for talks and workshops on AI-driven design, enterprise UX, and design leadership."
>
  <section class="border-b border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">Speaking & Workshops</h1>
      <p>
        I design immersive sessions for leaders and product teams who want to build experiences that adapt with their
        users. Each engagement draws from live enterprise programs, the <em>Stay Unfinished</em> methodology, and
        practical stories that make change tangible.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="mailto:hello@haiderali.co" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-gray-300 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 transition hover:border-gray-400 hover:bg-gray-50">hello@haiderali.co</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Book a session</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="space-y-10 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Keynote Topics</h2>
      <ul class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">AI with a Human Compass</strong>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">How to operationalize AI in enterprise products without sacrificing trust, clarity, or accountability.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Building Living Design Systems</strong>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Lessons from scaling design governance, tokens, and component libraries across 100+ teams.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">Leadership in Constant Change</strong>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Rituals and narratives that keep teams learning faster than their environment shifts.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <strong class="text-gray-900">The Stay Unfinished Loop</strong>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Why launching unfinished work is the only way to build products that remain relevant.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Workshop Formats</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Half-day intensives</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">Designed for leadership teams and cross-functional squads who need alignment fast.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Design Systems in Motion — operating models, adoption, and measurement.</li>
            <li>AI Product Blueprint — mapping the human + machine workflow and ethics guardrails.</li>
            <li>Outcome Roadmapping — connect OKRs with discovery and delivery rituals.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">90-minute labs</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">Interactive sessions for teams who want a spark to kick-start a broader initiative.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
            <li>Designing with AI prompts and guardrails.</li>
            <li>Story-driven stakeholder alignment.</li>
            <li>Experiment scorecards for data-informed iteration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Advisory Retainers</h3>
          <p class="mt-2">Quarterly partnerships for leaders who want an external design exec to challenge, coach, and co-create.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Who I work with</h2>
      <ul class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">Chief digital, product, and design officers building experience-led organizations.</li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">Enterprise product teams integrating AI into mission-critical workflows.</li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">Innovation labs and accelerators spinning up new service models.</li>
        <li class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-4">Conferences and communities seeking stories that go beyond theory.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-gray-200 py-16">
    <div class="space-y-6 text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Let's shape your next session</h2>
      <p>
        Share your audience, goals, and timeline. I tailor every talk to the maturity of your team and the outcomes you need.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0A84FF] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#086cd1]">Book a session</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

